# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the two main political parties have begun campaigning for next month 's elections , both hoping for a decisive victory that will break their balkan country 's post-communist governmental gridlock .
# ::alignments
(b / begin-01
      :ARG0 (p / political-party
            :quant 2
            :mod (m / main))
      :ARG1 (c / campaign-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (e / elect-01
                  :time (m2 / month
                        :mod (n / next))))
      :ARG0-of (c2 / cause-01
            :ARG1 (h / hope-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (w / win-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG0-of (b2 / break-01
                              :ARG1 (g / gridlock-01
                                    :ARG1 (g2 / government-organization
                                          :ARG0-of (g3 / govern-01)
                                          :mod (e2 / ethnic-group
                                                :name (n2 / name
                                                      :op1 "Balkans")))
                                    :time (a / after
                                          :op1 (p2 / political-movement
                                                :name n2
                                                :op1 "communism")))))
                  :mod (d / decisive))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok oil income of the gulf cooperation council -lrb- gcc -rrb- states will hit a record in nearly a decade due to higher oil prices , according to the emirates industrial bank -lrb- eib -rrb- .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (b / bank
            :mod (ii / industry)
            :mod (c / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Iran")))
      :ARG1 (h / hit-02
            :ARG0 (ii2 / income
                  :source (c2 / council
                        :topic (c3 / cooperate-01)
                        :mod (w / world-region
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Gulf")))
                  :mod (o / oil))
            :ARG1 (r / record)
            :ARG1-of (c4 / cause-01
                  :ARG0 (p / price-01
                        :ARG1 (o2 / oil)
                        :ARG1-of (h2 / have-degree-91
                              :ARG2 (h3 / high-02)
                              :ARG3 (m / more))))
            :time (a / after
                  :op1 (n3 / now)
                  :quant (n4 / nearly
                        :op1 (t / temporal-quantity
                              :quant 1
                              :unit (d / decade))))))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok in a major step toward severing kosovo 's remaining ties with yugoslavia , the united nations announced friday that the german mark will replace the yugoslav dinar as kosovo 's official currency .
# ::alignments
(a / announce-01
      :ARG0 (n / nation
            :ARG1-of (u / unite-01))
      :ARG1 (r / replace-01
            :ARG0 (m / mark
                  :mod (c / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Germany")))
            :ARG1 (d / dinar
                  :mod (c2 / country
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Yugoslavia")))
            :ARG2 (c3 / currency
                  :mod (o / official)
                  :poss c2))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday))
      :ARG4-of (s / step-01
            :ARG1 n
            :ARG2 (s2 / sever-01
                  :ARG0 n
                  :ARG1 (t / tie-01
                        :ARG1 c2
                        :ARG2 c2
                        :ARG1-of (r2 / remain-01)))
            :ARG1-of (m2 / major-02)))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok following ## days of fierce competition among six bidders , the combined bids tendered for five licenses for third-generation -lrb- g# -rrb- mobile phones had totaled nt$ ##.# billion , nt$ ##.# billion above the base price .
# ::alignments
(t / total-01
      :ARG1 (b / bid-01
            :quant 5
            :ARG1 (p / phone
                  :mod (m / mobile)
                  :mod (g / generation
                        :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                              :value 3)))
            :ARG1-of (c / combine-01))
      :ARG2 (m2 / monetary-quantity
            :quant 1000000000
            :unit (d / dollar))
      :ARG3 (a / above
            :op1 (m3 / monetary-quantity
                  :quant 1000000000
                  :unit (d2 / dollar)))
      :ARG1-of (f / follow-01
            :ARG2 (d3 / day
                  :time-of (c2 / compete-02
                        :ARG0 (c3 / company
                              :quant 6
                              :ARG0-of b))
                  :mod (f2 / fierce))))

# ::id 4 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok new york - heriberto seda waited nearly two years to dispute the charge that he is the zodiac killer , a violent criminal who preyed on the vulnerable and who terrorized new york city in two separate crime sprees in the early ####s .
# ::alignments
(w / wait-01
      :ARG1 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Heriberto"
                  :op2 "Saya")
            :mod (c / city
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "New"
                        :op2 "York")))
      :ARG2 (d / dispute-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG2 (c2 / charge-05
                  :ARG1 p
                  :ARG2 (a / and
                        :op1 (k / kill-01
                              :ARG0 p
                              :ARG1 (z / zodiac))
                        :op2 (c3 / criminal
                              :mod (v / violent)
                              :ARG0-of (p2 / prey-01
                                    :ARG1 (p3 / person
                                          :ARG1-of (v2 / vulnerable-01)))
                              :ARG0-of (t / terrorize-01
                                    :ARG1 c
                                    :manner (s / spree
                                          :quant 2
                                          :mod (c4 / crime-02)
                                          :ARG1-of (s2 / separate-02)
                                          :time (e / early))))))
            :duration (n3 / nearly
                  :op1 (t2 / temporal-quantity
                        :quant 2
                        :unit (y / year)))))

# ::id 5 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

      :ARG0 (a / and
            :op1 (p / person
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Pamela"
                        :op2 "Jelimo")
                  :ARG0-of (w / win-01
                        :ARG1 (j2 / jackpot
                              :mod (g / golden)
                              :mod (c / country
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Kenya")))
                        :mod (e / event
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Olympics"))))
            :op2 (p2 / person
                  :name (n4 / name
                        :op1 "Paulo"
                        :op2 "Jelimo")
                  :ARG0-of (w2 / win-01
                        :ARG1 j2)
                  :mod (c2 / country
                        :name (n5 / name
                              :op1 "Australia"))))
      :ARG1 (c3 / country)
      :ARG4 (r / reception
            :ARG1-of (s / stampede-02))
      :direction (b / back)
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday)
            :dayperiod (n6 / night)))

# ::id 6 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

      :ARG0 (d / data

                  :time (d2 / date-entity
                        :weekday (m / monday))))
      :ARG1 (s / signal-07
            :ARG1 (f / fall-01
                  :ARG1 (a / and
                        :op1 (a2 / activity-06
                              :ARG1 (m2 / manufacture-01))
                        :op2 (a3 / approve-01
                              :ARG1 (h / house-01)))
                  :ARG1-of (o / offset-01
                        :ARG0 (b / boost-01
                              :ARG1 (ii / inventory
                                    :mod (b2 / business))
                              :ARG0-of (l / lead-03
                                    :ARG2 (f2 / forecast-01
                                          :ARG1 (g / grow-01
                                                :ARG1 (e / economy))
                                          :ARG1-of (r2 / revise-01)))))
                  :ARG3 (e2 / economy
                        :mod (c / country
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "Australia")))
                  :ARG1-of (m3 / mix-01))))

                              :mod (r2 / recent)))
                  :ARG0-of (m / maim-01
                        :ARG1 c2)
                  :ARG0-of (d / defy-01
                        :ARG1 (f / force
                              :mod (s3 / security)
                              :quant (m2 / multiple
                                    :op1 1000)
                              :location (c3 / city
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "Baghdad")))))
            :location (c4 / country
                  :name (n4 / name
                        :op1 "Iraq"))))

                        :ARG1 (j / job))))

            :weekday (f / friday))
      :manner (t / take-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (a / appeal-03
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (b2 / belt
                        :mod (r / rust)
                        :ARG1-of (r2 / rack-01
                              :ARG0 (r3 / recession-02))

                              :name (n4 / name

                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (r4 / recapture-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG1 (e3 / excite-01
                              :ARG0 (c4 / campaign-01
                                    :ARG0 p))))))
